{"tid":564884,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無咩成語或詞語，細個時候係理解錯咗","createTime":"2018-02-18T12:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T21:07:26.000Z","uid":39623,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"932c93d48ad6963f9fb1e46ba827fb5f090b0b34","tid":564884,"uid":39623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉先<br />\n細個聽奉子成婚，以為係奉旨成婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時聽到啲親戚話奉子成婚，<br />\n可能睇得tvb故裝多，重諗住會接聖旨<br />\n然後由政府安排婚姻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ce8d5461ad95aeb6d5d43c4fcb5adf9de3f96e","tid":564884,"uid":147264,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"細個成日搞亂指腹為婚同奉子成婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb07a08f81bba1ab6ec715c89b08b72a98399a99","tid":564884,"uid":56240,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"工展會一連三日...<br />\n成日以為一年三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398b69f3cc56167ecf17d6751809c34da9f6fd73","tid":564884,"uid":4574,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"每況愈下<br />\n可圈可點<br />\n<br />\n中文老師教錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6196d2e62c7645342429851719fe60aa601463d3","tid":564884,"uid":6275,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"其貌不揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a646a6e889f2a7d0bc803d065704d32e2050ac","tid":564884,"uid"