>\n留翻一次佢中文堂比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d569cd4e9cba28c8975f44a87d44c982227481","tid":564884,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T18:37:47.000Z","msg":"細個聽到電視話仝人鞠躬、仝人祝賀<br />\n心諗點解窮人要同我鞠躬，要同我祝賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明咁大間公司但扮窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}